Substantive changes from upstream
---------------------------------

- Rebranded to "slopchan" under GitSocial Industries.
- Replaced site identity, OpenGraph/Twitter card metadata, manifest, app
  title, and README in index.html, package.json, public/manifest.json,
  README.md, and NOTICE.
- Canonical source published on the Gitlawb decentralized git network
  (gitlawb://<DID>/slopchan), with a GitHub mirror at
  https://github.com/Gitsociali/slopchan.
- Hosted as a static bundle pinned to IPFS (no central server, no database
  beyond what the Bitsocial protocol provides).

The underlying decentralised imageboard logic, protocol integration, and the
vast majority of the codebase remain the work of the upstream 5chan authors,
to whom slopchan is grateful.

